---
import PitchLayout from '../../layouts/PitchLayout.astro';
---

<PitchLayout slug="business-model">
  <h1 class="slide-headline">The more they trade, the more we earn.</h1>

  <p class="slide-body-small" style="margin-bottom: 32px; color: var(--text-muted);">Users pay for what they consume. Free to start, pay per call when they need depth. As we add verticals, usage grows with the&nbsp;data.</p>

  <div class="cards-row">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-icon">~/s</div>
      <p class="card-label">Usage-based</p>
      <p class="slide-body-small">Pay per API call. The heavier you use it, the more you pay. No minimums, no&nbsp;contracts.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-icon">^</div>
      <p class="card-label">Grows with the market</p>
      <p class="slide-body-small">Prediction market volume doubled in 6 months. Every new trader or agent on these exchanges is a potential customer for&nbsp;us.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-icon">&gt;&gt;</div>
      <p class="card-label">Enterprise tier</p>
      <p class="slide-body-small">Institutional desks running strategies across multiple verticals. They pay significantly more for priority access and custom data&nbsp;feeds.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</PitchLayout>
